      "role": "user",
      "content": "The \"evolving with new data\" angle is a good start, but the reporter is being really aggressive. They specifically asked why the candidate's floor vote last month was the complete opposite of what they're saying now. If we say it was just 'reassessing,' they're going to call us out for being dishonest about the previous position. Can we frame it so it doesn't look like they're backtracking on what they previously promised?",
